.DT
wear_armour
Discworld combat help
wear_armour

Name
.SI 5
wear_armour - Wears the armour.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
string wear_armour(object ob);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This function does all of the wearing othe armour.  It is the internal
function called by the monster/player command 'wear'.  It returns 0
if it suceeds or a string (which is the error message) if it fails.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
remove_armour, query_armours
.EP
